snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedApi, PlainObject

client = AsyncSeedApi(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.test_group.test_method_name(
        path_param="path_param",
        request=PlainObject(),
    )


asyncio.run(main())
